panels.name: Traffic Volume and Bytes Served
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| where size != "-"
| timeslice 10 buckets
| (size/(1048576*1000)) as gbytes 
| count as hits, sum(gbytes) as gbytes by _timeslice 
| sort _timeslice asc

panels.name: Traffic Distribution by Server
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| timeslice 10 buckets
| count by _timeslice, _sourceHost  
| transpose row _timeslice column _sourceHost

panels.name: Visitor Locations
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = src_ip
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code
| sort _count

panels.name: Responses Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| if(status_code matches "2*", 1, 0) as successes 
| if(status_code matches "3*", 1, 0) as redirects 
| if(status_code matches "4*", 1, 0) as client_errors 
| if(status_code matches "5*", 1, 0) as server_errors 
| timeslice 10 buckets 
| sum(successes) as successes, sum(client_errors) as client_errors,  sum(redirects) as redirects, sum(server_errors) as server_errors by _timeslice
| sort by _timeslice asc

panels.name: Popular Mobile Device Versions
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare ( iphone or ipad or android or samsung) 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| parse regex "\((?<device>iPhone).+? CPU iPhone OS (?<version>.+?) like Mac"  nodrop 
| parse regex "\((?<device>iPad).+? CPU OS (?<version>.+?) like Mac"  nodrop 
| parse regex " (?<device>Android) (?<version>[\d\.]+)" nodrop 
| parse regex "(?<device>SAMSUNG).+?(?<version>(?:GT-\w+|SGH-\w+|SPH-\w+|SCH-\w+))" 
| where device != ""
| count as count by device, version 
| sort count 
| limit 10

panels.name: Top 10 PC and Mac Versions
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare   ("macintosh" OR "mac os" OR "windows" OR "i686" or "PC" or ("Linux" AND !android))   
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<os>Mac OS) (?<version>[^;\)]+?)(?:;|\))" nodrop 
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<os>Windows)(?: NT | )(?<version>[\d.]+)" nodrop 
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<os>Linux) (?<version>\S+?)(?:\)|;)" nodrop 
| where os != ""
| count as count by os, version
| sort count 
| limit 10

panels.name: Vistor Platforms
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| if (user_agent matches "*iPad*" OR user_agent matches "*iPhone*" OR user_agent matches "*Android*" OR user_agent matches "*BlackBerry*" OR user_agent matches "*Galaxy*" OR user_agent matches "LGE-*" OR user_agent matches "SCH-*" OR user_agent matches "*HUAWEI-*" OR user_agent matches "*SAMSUNG*" OR user_agent matches "*samsung*" OR user_agent matches "Dalvik/*" OR user_agent matches "Nokia*" OR user_agent matches "LG-*" OR user_agent matches "*CFNetwork*"  OR user_agent matches "*UP.Browser/*" OR user_agent matches "*QQ*rowser*" OR user_agent matches "*NetFront/*" OR user_agent matches "*Windows Phone*" OR user_agent matches "*Mobile Safari*" OR user_agent matches "*iemobile*","Mobile","") as type
| if (user_agent matches "*Windows*" OR user_agent matches "*Win64*" OR user_agent matches "*Win32*" OR user_agent matches "*i686*" OR user_agent matches "*x86*","PC",type) as type
| if (user_agent matches "*Macintosh*" OR user_agent matches "*Mac OS*","Mac",type) as type
| if (type = "","bots/unknown",type) as type
| count type
| sort by _count

panels.name: Browsers and Operating Systems
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| if (user_agent matches "*Windows *" OR user_agent matches "*Win32*" OR user_agent matches "*Win64*","Windows","") as OS 
| if (user_agent matches "*Macintosh*" OR user_agent matches "*Darwin/*" OR user_agent matches "*Mac OS*","MacOS",OS) as OS 
| if (user_agent matches "* CrOS *","Chrome OS",OS) as OS
| if (user_agent matches "*Linux*","Linux",OS) as OS 
| if (user_agent matches "*iPad*","iPad",OS) as OS 
| if (user_agent matches "*iPhone*","iPhone",OS) as OS 
| if (user_agent matches "*Android*","Android",OS) as OS 
| if (user_agent matches "*Windows Phone*","Windows Phone",OS) as OS 
| if (OS == "","Other",OS) as OS 
| if (user_agent matches "Mozilla/*; rv:*)*","Mozilla","") as Browser
| if (user_agent matches "*MSIE*","Internet Explorer",Browser) as Browser 
| if (user_agent matches "*Firefox*","Firefox",Browser) as Browser 
| if (user_agent matches "*Safari*","Safari",Browser) as Browser 
| if (OS=="Android" AND user_agent matches "*WebKit*","WebKit",Browser) as Browser
| if ((OS=="iPhone" OR OS=="iPad") AND (user_agent matches "*Mobile/*" OR user_agent matches "*AppleWebKit*(KHTML*Gecko)*"),"Mobile Safari",Browser) as Browser
| if (browser == "" AND OS=="MacOS" AND user_agent matches "Mozilla/* (Macintosh;*(KHTML, like Gecko)*","Safari",Browser) as Browser 
| if (user_agent matches "*MobileSafari/*","Mobile Safari",Browser) as Browser
| if (user_agent matches "*Chrome*","Chrome",Browser) as Browser 
| if (user_agent matches "Opera*","Opera",Browser) as Browser 
| if (user_agent matches "Dolphin*","Dolphin",Browser) as Browser 
| if (Browser == "","Other",Browser) as Browser  
| count by OS,browser
| transpose row os column browser as *

panels.name: Visits by Country Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = src_ip
| where !isNull(country_name) and country_name != ""
| timeslice 5m
| count by _timeslice,country_name
| transpose row _timeslice column country_name as *

panels.name: Visits by US State Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent

| timeslice 5m
| where country_name = "United States" AND !isNull(region) AND region != ""
| count by _timeslice, region
| transpose row _timeslice column region as *

panels.name: Top 10 Search Terms from Popular Search Engines
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare  (google OR bing OR aol OR ask OR yahoo) ("p=" OR "q=" OR "wd=" OR "searchfor=")
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| parse regex field=referrer "(?:\?|&)(?:p|q|wd|searchfor)=(?<search_term>[^=]+?)(?:&|$)" nodrop 
| where search_term!=""
| urldecode(search_term)
| if(referrer matches "*google.*","Google","") as engine
| if(referrer matches "*bing.*","Bing",engine) as engine
| if(referrer matches "*ask.com*","Ask.com",engine) as engine
| if(referrer matches "*aol.*","AOL",engine) as engine
| if(referrer matches "*yahoo.*","Yahoo",engine) as engine
| where engine != "" 
| count as count by search_term
| sort count 
| limit 10

panels.name: Media Types Served
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| parse regex field=url "^/[^\?]+?\.(?<type>[a-zA-Z]{2,4})$" 
| parse regex field=url "/\S+?(?<email_prefix>(?:%40|@)[^.]+?)\.\w+" nodrop 
| where email_prefix="" 
| count as count by type

panels.name: Error Responses by Server
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare  
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| num(status_code) as status_code
| where status_code >= 400
| timeslice 5m
| count as count by _timeslice, _sourceHost
| transpose row _timeslice column _sourceHost

panels.name: Top 5 Clients Causing 4xx Errors
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare (40* OR 41* OR 42* OR 43* OR 44* or 45* or 49*) 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| where status_code matches "4*"
| count as count by src_ip
| sort count 
| limit 5

panels.name: Top 5 URIs causing 404 Responses
panels.queryString:

| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| where status_code="404"
| count as count by url
| sort count 
| limit 5

panels.name: Top 10 Bots Observed
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare ("Googlebot" OR "AskJeeves" OR "Digger" OR "Lycos"
OR "msnbot" OR "Inktomi Slurp" OR "Yahoo" OR "Nutch" OR "bingbot" OR
"BingPreview" OR "Mediapartners-Google" OR "proximic" OR "AhrefsBot" OR
"AdsBot-Google" OR "Ezooms" OR "AddThis.com" OR "facebookexternalhit" OR
"MetaURI" OR "Feedfetcher-Google" OR "PaperLiBot" OR "TweetmemeBot" OR
"Sogou web spider" OR "GoogleProducer" OR "RockmeltEmbedder" OR
"ShareThisFetcher" OR "YandexBot" OR "rogerbot-crawler" OR "ShowyouBot" OR "Baiduspider" OR "Sosospider" OR "Exabot")
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>facebook)externalhit?\W+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "Feedfetcher-(?<bot_name>Google?)\S+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>PaperLiBot?)/.+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>TweetmemeBot?)/.+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>msn?)bot\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Nutch?)-.+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Google?)bot\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "Feedfetcher-(?<bot_name>Google?)\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Yahoo?)!\s+Slurp[;/].+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>bing?)bot\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Bing?)Preview\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Sogou?)\s+web\s" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Yandex?)Bot\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>rogerbot?)\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>AddThis\.com?)\s+robot\s+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>ShareThis?)Fetcher/.+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Ahrefs?)Bot/.+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>MetaURI?)\s+API/.+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Showyou?)Bot\s+" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Google?)Producer;" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Ezooms?)\W" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Rockmelt?)Embedder\s+" nodrop 
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Sosospider?)\W" nodrop 
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Baidu?)spider" nodrop
| parse regex field=user_agent "(?<bot_name>Exabot?)\W"
| where bot_name != ""
| if (bot_name="bing","Bing",bot_name) as bot_name
| count as count by bot_name
| sort by count

panels.name: Server Errors Over Time
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare (50* or 51* or 52* or 53*)
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| where status_code matches "5*"
| timeslice 5m
| count as count by _timeslice,status_code
| transpose row _timeslice column status_code as *

panels.name: Non 200 Response Status Codes
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| where !(status_code matches "2*") 
| count as count by status_code 
| sort by count

panels.name: Client Locations - 4xx Errors
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$CloudFlare (40* OR 41* OR 42* OR 43* or 44* OR 45* or 49*) 
| json "ClientIP", "ClientRequestMethod", "ClientRequestURI", "CacheResponseStatus", "CacheResponseBytes", "ClientRequestReferer", "ClientRequestUserAgent" as src_ip, method, url, status_code, size, referrer, user_agent 
| where status_code matches "4*" 
| lookup latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code from geo://default on ip = src_ip
| count by latitude, longitude, country_code, country_name, region, city, postal_code, area_code, metro_code
| sort _count
